<p><span class="anchor" id="p19"></span>٢٩٣١ - ع، <span class="c2">(صح)</span> هشيم بن بشير <span class="c2">(٤: ٣٠٦/ ٩٢٥٠)</span>.<a href="#p19" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p20"></span>٢٩٣٢ - ع، <span class="c2">(صح)</span> همَّام بن يحيى <span class="c2">(٤: ٣٠٩/ ٩٢٥٣)</span>.<a href="#p20" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p21"></span>٢٩٣٣ - بخ ت، هود بن عبد الله العَصَري <span class="c2">(٤: ٣١٠/ ٩٢٥٥)</span>.<a href="#p21" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>